## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="95cc2-109">El siguiente código de C# utiliza `GetNode` para tener acceso a un nodo de la <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> se encuentra situado actualmente.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="95cc2-109">The following C# code uses `GetNode` to access a node the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> is currently positioned on.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
XmlDocument doc = new XmlDocument();  
doc.Load("books.xml");  
XPathNavigator nav =  doc.CreateNavigator();  
XmlNode node = ((IHasXmlNode)nav).GetNode();  
Console.WriteLine(node.LocalName);   
//You can edit the returned XmlNode.  
```
